## **💡 핵심 기술**

### **1️⃣ Loop Analyzer**

#### **기능**

```python
analyzer = LoopAnalyzer()

# Bound 파싱
bounds = analyzer.parse_loop_bounds("0 <= i < n; 0 <= j < n")
# → [Bound(variable='i', lower=0, upper='n', stride=1), ...]

# 메모리 접근 추출
accesses = analyzer.extract_memory_accesses("A[i,j] = B[i,j] + C[i,j]")
# → [MemoryAccess(location='A[i,j]', access_type='WRITE'),
#    MemoryAccess(location='B[i,j]', access_type='READ'), ...]

# 의존성 감지
deps = analyzer.analyze_dependencies(accesses)
# → [Dependency(src='B[i,j]', tgt='A[i,j]', type='FLOW'), ...]
```

